                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-356317488" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="356317488">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/softclown/">Edmund</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2011-02-20</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">轻松易读 考据严谨</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="944795265">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-944795265" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-944795265" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="944795265">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/gaobiedeying/">子文东</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2015-07-28</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">读到一半，忍不住先感慨一下：除了有些文字太小，版面设计的整体感觉好赞！尤其是小图穿插在文字中的方式，很好的解决了读图会打断读文字的问题。而且作者很懂得如何用有趣的语言来介绍一些繁杂枯燥的理论，应该算是艺术设计类入门书的典范啊～</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="42065811">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-42065811" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-42065811" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="42065811">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/bighead/">大头绿豆</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2008-05-25</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">内容方面：杂俎，营养不少。可是枝蔓太多，都不深入，隔靴搔痒，很不解渴。装帧方面：插图大赞。字体选了太多，排版罗嗦，显小气了。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

        

